  Description: Your ancestors crossed the Crown of the World or resided on snowy
    peaks. You gain cold resistance equal to half your level (minimum 1). You treat
    environmental cold effects as if they were one step less extreme (incredible
    cold becomes extreme, extreme cold becomes severe, and so on). Your alternate
    form is a common Medium humanoid ancestry prevalent where you grew up (typically
    human), called a tailless form.
